Notes

1) to pending_write to ekana aneksartito apo to pote tha stalei i apantisi to b kanali, diladi tha dextw neo write molis staloun kai ta teleutaia data sto ahb, amesws tote tha mporw na dextw neo transaction kai dn koitaw to b kanali.
opote isws xreiastei mia fifo sto b kanali

antitheta sta read perimenw na fygoun kai ta teleutaia read data apo to r kanali prin parw allo transaction gt fantazomai oti ekei dn tha ithela na valw mia fifo me read data

2) na deiksw ston taso gia to busy kai to oti tote o slave katevazei to hready sto low gia na eimai sigouros oti douleuei kala